data.description: Embrace the charm of this lovely Ranch-style home that offers a comfortable and inviting living space. The living room features vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere perfect for relaxation. The bright kitchen includes a breakfast nook that leads out to a deck, making it an ideal spot for enjoying your morning coffee or meals with a view. The primary bedroom is generously sized and provides ample space for comfort and relaxation. The ensuite bathroom is both functional and stylish, featuring a double vanity for added convenience. A front porch provides a charming outdoor space where you can unwind and greet neighbors and friends. A workshop in the backyard offers a versatile space for hobbies, projects, or additional storage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your own!
